				  lohit-tamil
Current Version :- 2.91.3

* Wed Apr 26 2017 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.91.3
- Added appstream metadata file io.pagure.lohit.tamil.font.metainfo.xml

* Thu Mar 02 2017 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.91.2
- PR for python2 to 3 from ShaguftaMethwani and mandarvaze.
- Updated Makefile to call script from fontforge rather than python.

* Mon Dec 01 2014 Pravin Saitpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.91.1
- Lohit Tamil 2.91.0 hinting issues #56 
- Testing on WinXP and identified some issues. (See README)

* Thu Sep 17 2014 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.91.0
- First release of Tamil after re-writing all rules.
Technical improvements
- Supports taml and tml2 open type script tags.
- Follows AGL specification syntax.
- Open type rules are available in .fea file for easy reusability
- Open type gsub lookups reduction from 5 to 4.
- Corrected glyph class of all glyphs.
- Renamed anchors to taanchor.
Designing improvements
- "Copy Reference" feature implemented for better reusability of glyphs.
- Improved grid fitting(GASP) table.
- Auto Hinting from fontforge
Testing
- Tested with Harfbuzz NG and Uniscribe (W8)
- Test file available with release tarball
- Auto test integrated with Makefile ($make test).

* Fri Dec 21 2012 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.5.3
- Dropping RFN from OFL.txt
- updated Zero and Five numeral
- updated shapes of u0BF9 Tamil Rupee Sign patch from Shriramana Sharma <samjnaa@gmail.com>
- fixed Rendering of Letter RA,RI,RII per GoTN standards #829143
- Skipped version 2.5.2 for matching with family version

* Tue Jun 05 2012 Pravin Satpute <psatpute@redhat.com> - 2.5.1
- improved asterisk glyph
- added autohint instructions in .conf file
- removed self intersecting error from latin shapes
- corrected SHI SHII glyphs #806591
- improved numbers, patch from Shriramana Sharma <samjnaa@gmail.com>
- Check New font Lohit Tamil Classical, released in another tarball lohit-tamilclassical

